Value local_if ([^\]]+)
Value neighbor_name (.+)
Value neighbor_port (.+)
Value chassis_id (.+)
Value mgmt_ip (\S+)

Start
  ^\s*\[${local_if}\]\s*$$ -> Record
  ^\s*System\s+name\s*:\s*${neighbor_name}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^\s*Port\s+ID\s*:\s*${neighbor_port}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^\s*Chassis\s+ID\s*:\s*${chassis_id}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^\s*Management\s+address\s*:\s*${mgmt_ip}\s*$$ -> Record

